Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神核心被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心控制下的奴獸已被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神部隊全部機能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲到此為止了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這座城市為新大陸\N讓一切結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經無法回頭了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體貼的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體貼過頭的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我現在要感謝你的體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你留力量給我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古風琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.57,0:01:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第26話\NDream☆Wing～夢想所在～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪打算把這座城市一起毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要創造一個\N大家都能笑口常開的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不會逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:01:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，把生命交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我得行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妮娜在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的性命與妳同在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算蒼天的力量覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠妳一個人還是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我稍微活躍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是，一上場就做苦工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到青色貴石的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到一同前進的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我實踐妳最後的遺言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導之星呀，就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傳說竟然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當引導之星閃耀紅光時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的乙HiME…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將擺脫“乙式”的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優真的做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在將妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從命運之軛解放開來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞鬥服竟在沒認證下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請選擇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以妳們自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事到現在還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，慢著啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅莎麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·們·吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，也請讓我們加入您的麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們不能以自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定現在該做什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會撐住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了，乙HiME們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止那座古風琴！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好賊喔，那是犯規吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市北邊出現新的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於連退路也沒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓原始奴獸全部啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（遵從黑色誓約，我將實現盟約）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（古代之光，知識與智慧之神啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（請賜我忠實的奴僕吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹妳們到城裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留，拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME需要的是力量，技巧和…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅力！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N來把過去的比試了斷一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比比看誰打倒得最多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真是沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你們一網大魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙\N我已經不知道妳要講什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？閣下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海拉德少尉，這給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已確實收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在此準備進城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妮娜就交給妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:06:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色捲捲藍色捲捲黃色捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳穿上舞鬥服根本沒意義嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉妳閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪亞姊姊？五柱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，妳還是乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直被追著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易終於有機會了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿和\N卻得繼位成為卡迪亞王而被帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我則被瑪亞姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正，讓她跟阿和陛下締結契約
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是抵銷了這次的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不讓妳們上床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不死心！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算過了這麼久\N妳還是有欠優雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易老到理想年齡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在居然還得現出這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這種地方都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去將編織者…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將妮娜從古風琴上解放開來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座管風琴\N要是演奏太久會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下通路有舞鬥服反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蒼天的青玉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是停下古風琴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親為了我捨棄自己的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會賭上我的一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋一定會說他並不想\N為了求生而害妮娜做出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又知道什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟父親的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道些什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微…知道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡…謝爾蓋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我察覺到自己的心意時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法思考其他事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜的心情也是…什麼都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算犧牲一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拿世界來交換
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要那個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…我絕對要阻止妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能在一旁守著她們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就要靠她們自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是得將世界的結局\N交給乙HiME之間的戰爭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過契約好像解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就只能看戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算只讓愛莉卡奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪，停止古風琴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個只聽妮娜的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是真正的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想把這個世界\N恢復成原本的模樣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也覺得很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲乙HiME，又封印科學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這星球\N曾因為這玩意兒毀滅過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我會好好照顧它的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免得它失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣什麼都沒改變到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走回頭路？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學也要漸漸開放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會不需要乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不會是你多管閒事下的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得要有人管理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信可以的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是為了什麼而戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要創造一個\N大家都能笑口常開的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種作夢般的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就因為是夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次來到這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇見妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到靜留姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才真正想當一個乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我現在成為乙HiME了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那時我沒有夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不會成為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼亂來的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要相信它，就會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得相信它會實現而前進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然什麼都不會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為妳沒有真正受挫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有真正犯錯過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再努力思考\N重新來過就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣又可以再向前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都太遲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死心呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也喜歡大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我無法放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很笨，什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我想更加瞭解妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們再一起重新開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好，妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能多聊聊就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟埃爾斯…還有愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來得及啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里…香…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，那傢伙失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去又會跟之前一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了維持謝爾蓋的命\N而不斷運轉的古風琴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經超過界限了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，那古風琴的力量與記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正流向妮娜的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類製作那個所犯下的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖與憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有如過去被稱為\N“純白無暇金剛石”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因絕望而徹底染黑一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來以為\N在變成這樣之前可以結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我賭輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是現在不打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界會完蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳…當我是朋友的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪，快叫它停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過度掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說沒用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴，哪能放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說是不是，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，真白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳…愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:18:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪·戴·阿爾泰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉審議會臨時法庭之命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快送去加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然不該存在於這個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於抓到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里…香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此對人民宣誓以上事項
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，最後收尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK，看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡完工了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然目前還是座小城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，要從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早呢，以後的路還很長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧，咪咪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，愛莉卡，開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.86,0:22:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.40,0:23:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就只是妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好，謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


